These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, hot-chocolate, mirinda, juice
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, photographer, scientist, writer
City: marseilles, hannover, boston, edinburgh
4 different pets are kept: cat, fish, frog, rabbit
1. the photographer is the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the person traveling to boston is the designer##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the right of the photographer##1
5. the scientist is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
6. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
7. the photographer is the owner of the cat##1
8. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
9. the person drinking juice is on the left of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage         | lemonade  | juice  | hot-chocolate | mirinda |
| Job           | photographer | designer | writer  | scientist  |
| City   | edinburgh       | boston      | marseilles | hannover      |
| Pet           | cat          | fish     | frog    | rabbit     |

