.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, electrician, writer, pilot
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, kiwi, orange, papaya
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, folk, indie, soul
4 different pets are kept: horse, snake, turtle, goldfish
1. the person eating broccoli is on the far right##1
2. the fan of soul is the owner of the horse##1
3. the person eating orange is on the right of the project-manager##1
4. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
5. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
6. the writer is the fan of indie##1
7. the fan of folk is on the left of the electrician##1
8. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the project-manager##1
9. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Job      | writer     | project-manager       | electrician | pilot        |
| Food          | papaya     | kiwi       | orange   | broccoli   |
| Music-Genre   | indie      | folk       | soul     | dubstep    |
| Pet         | turtle | goldfish | horse | snake |

