3. the fan of ambient is on the far right##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
5. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
6. the fan of funk is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
8. the australian is on the far right##1
9. the person who growslily is the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Sport           | skateboarding   | volleyball  | parkour | ice-hockey |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | funk       | d&b       | ambient     |
| Nationality   | thai       | turkish    | dutch     | australian  |
| Flower           | begonia     | lily | tulip     | daisy         |

