5. the turkish is on the right of the person driving the train##1
6. the person driving the train is the thai##1
7. the french is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
8. the social-worker is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
9. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the teacher##1

.:: Answer ::.
