 5. the person drinking juice is the writer##1
 6. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 7. the doctor is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 9. the doctor is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Sport          | skateboarding  | parkour | swimming     | badminton |
| Job           | doctor  | writer      | accountant | dancer    |
| Beverage   | coffee | juice  | iced-tea    | 7up  |
