 4. the owner of the frog is on the left of the australian##1
 5. the russian is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 6. the australian is on the left of the malaysian##1
 7. the owner of the bird is the person driving the scooter##1
 8. the farmhouse house is on the far left##1
 9. the farmhouse house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
10. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| House    | farmhouse | townhouse     | ranch-style    | cottage |
| Nationality       | spanish | australian    | malaysian | russian |
| Pet         | frog   | hedgehog  | pony        | bird    |
| Transport   | taxi   | quad-bike | airplane    | scooter |

