5. the person eating onion is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
6. the person eating peas is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
7. the freelancer is the owner of the goat##1
8. the owner of the horse is the person drinking 7up##1
9. the owner of the ferret is the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |     4      |
