3. the fan of classical is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the person drinking milk is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person playing poker##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person playing domino##1
7. the person drinking milk is the owner of the frog##1
8. the fan of disco is on the far left##1
9. the fan of metal is the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| Game         | whist | domino | mah-jongg | poker     |
| Music-Genre   | disco   | metal       | blues       | classical  |
