.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, lemonade, tea
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, brown, fuchsia, white
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, egyptian, indian, malaysian
4 different games are played: poker, backgammon, snooker, whist
1. the person who likes white is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
