3. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is the person who likes white##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the left of the egyptian##1
6. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
7. the malaysian is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
8. the person who likes brown is the person drinking tea##1
9. the argentine is on the right of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | coffee     | tea           | juice    | lemonade    |
| Color         | fuchsia  | brown | grey  | white |
| Nationality   | indian     | argentine     | egyptian | malaysian   |
| Game         | whist | poker     | backgammon | snooker     |

